Global Mobile Campaign Management Platform Market Insights
Mobile Campaign Management Platform Market size was valued at USD 8.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 15.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Mobile Campaign Management Platform Market Overview
The global Mobile Campaign Management Platform market is valued at approximately $7.4 billion in 2025 and is expected to expand at a compounded annual growth rate (CAGR) of 15.3% during the forecast period. The growing demand for personalized mobile marketing, the increasing penetration of smartphones, and the shift towards digital advertising are the primary factors driving market growth. Additionally, the adoption of automation tools to manage and optimize campaigns on mobile devices is gaining traction among businesses aiming for higher engagement and conversion rates. The market is experiencing rapid advancements in artificial intelligence, machine learning, and data analytics to enable better targeting and optimization of campaigns.

